Package org.jboss.windup.reporting.ruleexecution

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RuleExecutionInformationForReading
    Provides access to RuleExecutionInformation data
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FormatRule
    Formats the provided rule for printing in an HTML report.
    GetAllRuleProviders
    Returns a List of all AbstractRuleProviders loaded by Windup.
    GetRuleExecutionResults
    Returns information about which Rules have been evaluated by windup as well as their execution results.
    RuleExecutionInformation
    Contains information about a Rule and how it was executed by Windup (whether it was evaluated and executed, whether it failed, and various statistics on what it performed.
    RuleExecutionResultsListener
    Manages recording the history of Rules executed by Windup.
